{
  "stem": "22047.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we were trying to develop a mono-propellant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were using nitromethane.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nitromethane, as you may know, is used in race cars-- [LAUGHS] high-powered race cars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, so we were trying to develop this nitromethane assist takeoff unit engine, and we had all kinds of fun with that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One time, we had an explosion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it tore the engine off the test stand and threw it for half a mile.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked at, at Aerojet as a test engineer for a long time, and then got into working on other kinds of propulsion types of programs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Spent, let's see, from 1951 till 1964 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] working on various kinds of propulsion devices.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One for an ICBM, which was the Titan ICBM, intercontinental ballistic missile.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Aerojet was responsible for the engines on that, and I, I designed and, and had built elements of those engines, gas generators, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I was offered a, a position at Jet Propulsion Laboratory in Pasadena.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where my experience in unmanned spacecraft came to fore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- after I accepted the offer and went to work at JPL, I was assigned to, to monitor and direct the contract with an organization in New Jersey called Thiokol, who was building the rocket engines for the Surveyor spacecraft, which was a moon lander.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the preamble to the Apollo program.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We sent up-- actually built, built seven spacecraft.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Actually, JPL didn't build them, but we were the contractors and had Hughes Aircraft in El Segundo build them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We sent seven up, and five were successful and landed on the moon and found out a lot about the moon.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
